    • initialize

      public void initialize(URL url, ResourceBundle resourceBundle)
      Initialize method which initializes the Reports controller class.

      Each of the combo boxes is initialized based on the data received from the client_schedule database

      This method utilizes three lambda expressions which promote better code readability and reduce the amount of code required. With each lambda expression utilizing only one line of code, their functionality can be easily understood.

      Specified by:
      initialize in interface javafx.fxml.Initializable
      Parameters:
      url - The FXML location used to resolve relative paths for the root object, or null if the location is not known.
      resourceBundle - The resources used to localize the root object, or null if the root object was not localized.
